@startuml sequence_order
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Parts Order Submission

actor "Fleet Manager" as User
participant "Angular SPA\n(Kendo UI)" as FE
participant "CartController\n(.NET 8+)" as Cart
participant "PartsOrdersController\n(.NET 8+)" as Orders
participant "OrderHandler\n(MediatR)" as Handler
participant "NotificationService\n(SignalR + Email)" as Notif
database "SQL Server 2022" as DB

== Add Items to Cart ==

User -> FE: Search & select part
FE -> Cart: POST /api/v1/cart/items\n{partId, quantity}
Cart -> DB: Validate part exists\n& availability != OutOfStock
Cart -> DB: INSERT CartItem
Cart --> FE: 201 Created (CartItem)
FE --> User: Cart badge updated

User -> FE: Adjust quantity
FE -> Cart: PUT /api/v1/cart/items/{id}\n{quantity: 3}
Cart -> DB: UPDATE CartItem quantity
Cart --> FE: 200 OK

== Review Cart ==

User -> FE: Open cart
FE -> Cart: GET /api/v1/cart
Cart -> DB: SELECT CartItems\nJOIN Parts (for prices)
Cart --> FE: Cart items + subtotal
FE --> User: Display cart with\nquantity adjusters

== Submit Order ==

User -> FE: Click "Submit Order"
FE -> Orders: POST /api/v1/parts/orders
Orders -> Handler: SubmitOrderCommand
Handler -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
Handler -> DB: SELECT CartItems\nfor current user
Handler -> DB: INSERT PartsOrder\n(generate PO-YYYYMMDD-NNN)
Handler -> DB: INSERT OrderLineItems\n(snapshot price, calc totals)
Handler -> DB: DELETE CartItems\nfor current user
Handler -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
Handler -> Notif: Dispatch order confirmation\n(email + in-app)
Handler --> Orders: OrderResult
Orders --> FE: 201 Created\n{orderNumber, lineItems, subtotal}
FE --> User: Order confirmation\nwith order number

@enduml
